title: Jim Jefferies / Hemorrhoid Surgery, Diverticulitis, & Glandular Fever
description: Priyanka explains PRP (platelet-rich plasma) to Sean so he can finally understand what his doctors injected into his knee. Jim Jefferies talks out of his ***hole about his hemorrhoids and diverticulitis and how his first kiss turned into Glandular Fever (mono).
